Implemented the duplicate-option fix.

`Autocomplete` now supports `getOptionKey`, so duplicate labels can use a stable unique key:

```jsx
<Autocomplete
  options={options}
  getOptionLabel={(option) => option.name}
  getOptionKey={(option) => option.id}
/>
```

